text: Sybra iconica is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Pascoe in 1865.BioLib.cz - Sybra iconica. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. It contains two subspecies, Sybra iconica clarevitticollis and Sybra iconica iconica. ==References== iconica Category:Beetles described in 1865
title: Sybra iconica
